        <h3 class="text-lg md:text-xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4">KVKK UYARINCA YAPILAN TANIMLAMALAR</h3>
        <p><strong>Veri Sorumlusu :</strong> DENTALIMPLANT CLINIC TRAKYA SAĞLIK HİZM. LTD. ŞTİ.’yi<br>
